data.description: Upgrades abound throughout this home...Water softener and water filtration system, A/C unit for garage, with its own condenser, ($7K), 2 - 5 ton AC units and Heat compressors completely serviced, Total Kitchen remodel, $20K+, cabinets, granite, tile floor, and lighting, Oversized fully bricked backyard, with covered patio and fans, fire pit, marble benches, Plantation Shutters in Kitchen and Family Room, Family room with 2-way gas fireplace, Upgraded ceiling fans in bedrooms, cafe nook, formal dining room, family room, Security System, Hardwood floors in the family room, stairs, upstairs hallway, main floor bedroom, Fan lights installed along the upstairs hallway, Slra window screens, Fully insulated attic floor (6-9 inches), Attic Fans, Side patio w/pond - unfinished but plumbed.  Easy access to the freeway and near the VA Hospital, Walmart, Smith's, Home Depot, Kohl's, YMCA & LV Motor Speedway
